AB  - In this article we consider models deduced from a latent regression model by a non-linear mapping (probit, tobit, disequilibrium models, …). In this context we define simulated residuals whose role is similar to that of usual residuals in the regression model. In particular it is possible, with these new tools, to use the standard regression packages for diagnostic checks or genuine statistical tests.
